RipHop 4 Life

Bought this today at Hot Topic so I could get the poster and art. Love "This Addiction"! The best indie group with a a major following and genuine hip-hop AND punk roots. See them live and show love for these guy - living proof that dedication and commitment can pay off. I am a 40 Punk Rocker who loves this album.
